In an attempt to contribute to the understanding of the anomaly, the Institute of Experimental and Applied Physics at the Czech Technical University in Prague is building a spectrometer with the aim to essentially repeat the original ATOMKI experiment, ie, to check the existence of the effect within the nuclear reaction induced by protons impinging on either 7Li\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
