				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$p+{^7\text {Li}}\rightarrow {^8\text {Be}}+a(17)$$\end{document} is expected to be zero (or negligible) due to absent (or extremely suppressed) magnetic multipole contributions.

